013package org.apache.juneau.examples.core.pojo;
014
015import org.apache.juneau.annotation.*;
016
017/**
018 * Sample pojo class.
019 *
020 * <ul class='seealso'>
021 * </ul>
022 */
023public class Pojo {
024   private final String id;
025   private final String name;
026
027   /**
028    * @param id The <bc>id</bc> property value.
029    * @param name The <bc>name</bc> property value.
030    */
031   @Beanc
032   public Pojo(@Name("id") String id, @Name("name") String name) {
033      this.id = id;
034      this.name = name;
035   }
036
037   /**
038    * @return The <bc>id</bc> property value.
039    */
040   public String getId() {
041      return id;
042   }
043
044   /**
045    * @return The <bc>name</bc> property value.
046    */
047   public String getName() {
048      return name;
049   }
050}
